Currently group search in Confluence is not intelligent and must match exactly. For example, to find the group "SecGrp-AWS-Admin-RelEng', one has to search for "secgrp" as shown in [^secgrp.png]. If one searches for "RelEng", no matches are found as shown in [^RelEng.png].

Many organizations have naming conversions for groups, e.g., a department is used in the front like "SecGrp", and the search can return hundreds of groups. If the search can partially match group names from any position, it will help to find 'SecGrp-AWS-Admin-RelEng' instantly.

